textBox.richText: This is summertime ! The biometric group is upgrading and disseminating. For left to right: Pavel Korshunov, André Anjos, Sushil Bhattacharjee, Guillaume Heusch, Sébastien Marcel, Manuel Günther (on the move to University of Colorado at Colorado Spring), Hannah Muckenhirn, Ivana Chingovska, Tiago de Freitas Pereira, Elie Khoury (moving soon to Pindrop Security ) and Laurent El-Shafey (moving soon to Google in Mountain View).
